{"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"RenderContext"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"RenderContext"}],"externalID":"s:8Workflow13RenderContextC","modules":[{"name":"Workflow"}],"symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class","role":"symbol","title":"RenderContext"},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/makeOutputSink()","doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/makeSink(of:)","doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/makeSink(of:onEvent:)","doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/makeStateMutationSink()","doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/runSideEffect(key:action:)"],"generated":true,"title":"Instance Methods","anchor":"Instance-Methods"}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RenderContext"},{"type":"text","text":" is the composition point for the workflow tree."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"RenderContext"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"WorkflowType"},{"kind":"text","text":"> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"where"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"WorkflowType"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/Workflow","preciseIdentifier":"s:8WorkflowAAP","text":"Workflow"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"During a render pass, a workflow may want to defer to a child","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"workflow to render some portion of its content. For example,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a workflow that renders to a split-screen view model might","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to child A for the left side, and child B for the right","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"side view models. Nesting allows for a fractal tree that is constructed","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"out of many small parts.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If a parent wants to delegate to a child workflow, it must first"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"create an instance of that workflow. This can be thought of as the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"model of the child workflow. It does not contain any active state,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it simply contains the data necessary to create or update a workflow"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"node."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The parent then calls "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"render(workflow:outputMap:)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with two values:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The child workflow.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A closure that transforms the child’s output events into the parent’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Event"},{"type":"text","text":" type so that the parent can respond to events generated by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the child."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the parent had previously rendered a child of the same type, the existing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"child workflow node is updated."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If the parent had not rendered a child of the same type in the previous","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"render pass, a new child workflow node is generated.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The infrastructure then performs a render pass on the child to obtain its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"Rendering","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" value, which is then returned to the caller.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/workflow\/rendercontext"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://Workflow/documentation/Workflow/RenderContext":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"RenderContext"}],"title":"RenderContext","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext","type":"topic","abstract":[{"code":"RenderContext","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is the composition point for the workflow tree."}],"url":"\/documentation\/workflow\/rendercontext","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"RenderContext"}]},"doc://Workflow/documentation/Workflow/RenderContext/makeSink(of:)":{"url":"\/documentation\/workflow\/rendercontext\/makesink(of:)","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Creates a ","type":"text"},{"code":"Sink","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" that can be used to send ","type":"text"},{"code":"Action","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"s.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"makeSink"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"Action"},{"kind":"text","text":">("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"of"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:8Workflow13RenderContextC8ma